outputs.output_descr:
The project will provide support towards advocacy, strategic policy advice and capacity development to targeted institutions for climate change.

Cognisant of the need to strengthen institutional capacities to scale up action on climate change. Support will focus on enhancing key upstream elements of low carbon  climate resilient development both at the national and local levels, by:
-	providing continued support to upstream capacity enhancement and leadership strengthening actions at the highest level in climate decision-making, in order to improve coordination, overall directions and enhance Ghana's capacity to participate effectively in global climate negotiations;
-	 enhancing access to vital information on climate change mitigation activities for investors, policy makers, researchers and other critical stakeholders to facilitate investments in low carbon strategies;
-	scaling up the CC/DRR mainstreaming process especially within urban planning efforts.
